{"tid":707921,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[想學嘢] 有冇人覺得人類嘅進化史好詭異","createTime":"2018-06-19T03:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T03:32:05.000Z","uid":172616,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b391b1b9d532f657d14f3cf8ad9eb5b0cfcf08","tid":707921,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"個世界咁大, 動物物種咁多, 點解一定係人類嘅前身先成功進化變成具有一定智慧嘅生物? <br />\n點解就唔可以係其他物種進化?<br />\n而人類進化咗幾千甚至幾萬年, 就真係冇可能有其他物種(例如:猿猴)等嘅生物進化到有智慧? <br />\n點解就一定係古人猿先成功進化? <br />\n生物嘅基因唔係本來就會慢慢適應環境然後進化咩? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 好奇心大, 大家一齊討論吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71d82d146cf3eb2bd881a6a99a213fc81303817","tid":707921,"uid":146435,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:30:36.000Z","msg":"創造論解釋人類起源會好d"},{"pid":"f6f7900e68d0a41deb87564314bc70729147eca2","tid":707921,"uid":810,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:31:56.000Z","msg":"係神既旨意☺️"},{"pid":"1e769b0e6a92dc343f6b4f1e16799fcdb21f38c8","tid":707921,"uid":172616,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b71d82d146cf3eb2bd881a6a99a213fc81303817","tid":707921,"uid":146435,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:30:36.000Z","msg":"創造論解釋人類起源會好d"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:33:51.000Z","msg":"即係話人類, 地球甚至宇宙都係由神/上帝/外星人所創造? <br />\n但佢地嘅目的係乜? 創造完擺喺到幾千萬幾十億萬年唔理又有咩意義?"},{"pid":"859f57966db020f811f1fe5b7ab1324d617e82d8","tid":707921,"uid":146435,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e769b0e6a92dc343f6b4f1e16799fcdb21f38c8","tid":707921,"uid":172616,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b71d82d146cf3eb2bd881a6a99a213fc81303817","tid":707921,"uid":146435,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:30:36.000Z","msg":"創造論解釋人類起源會好d"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:33:51.000Z","msg":"即係話人類, 地球甚至宇宙都係由神/上帝/外星人所創造? <br />\n但佢